130
00:10:00,130 --> 00:10:02,720
So you're my boyfriend now.

131
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:07,320
Can I trouble you again to clear this up?

132
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,420
Clear it up again?

133
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:11,240
It's fine for an ordinary person like me.

134
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:15,380
I'm afraid it might ruin the reputation of a celebrity like you.

135
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:20,470
