200
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:48,240
Stop minding other people's success and failures.

201
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:50,680
When are you going to get rid of that broken phone

202
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:53,440
and focus on GO and the competitions,

