214
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:07,460
And it wasn't embarrassing for you to confess at the banquet?

215
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:11,710
Stop mentioning what happened yesterday. I don't want to hear it.

216
00:15:11,710 --> 00:15:13,740
Is Brother Xu Chi here yet?

217
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:17,100
President Xu? He didn't come.

218
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:19,540
- I'm sure he's nursing his wound at home.
- Nursing his wound?

219
00:15:19,540 --> 00:15:22,630
What happened? Is he injured? Is he okay?

220
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:24,960
No way.

221
00:15:25,870 --> 00:15:28,280
Didn't your sister tell you?

222
00:15:36,610 --> 00:15:39,380
From the moment I met you when we were young, I liked you.

223
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:41,920
I was hopelessly in love with you.

224
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:44,030
I want to be with you.

225
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:47,340
- Are you willing?
- I'm sorry.

226
00:15:48,310 --> 00:15:52,600
Your face looks exactly like what President Xu looked like yesterday.

227
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:57,510
Such a big banquet, such a quiet venue.

228
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:01,410
