247
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:01,960
Okay. I'll see you at the movie theater.

248
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:04,790
- See you soon.
- Bye-bye.

249
00:18:20,200 --> 00:18:23,250
Why did you think to see this?

250
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:27,230
You don't like it?

251
00:18:28,760 --> 00:18:30,440
It's not that.

252
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:34,700
Actually, I've always wanted to see it again.

253
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:37,260
I just didn't want to see it by myself.

254
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:39,840
Thank you.

255
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,300
